# 🍕 Pizza Delivery Application

**Intern:** Utkarsh  
**Task:** Level 3 — Task 1  
**File:** `Pizza_app.html`

## 📌 Overview
A full-featured Pizza Delivery web application with User and Admin portals — menu browsing, custom pizza builder, cart, Razorpay test checkout, live order tracking, and admin dashboard.

## 🎯 Features
### 👤 User
- ✅ Register and Login
- ✅ Browse signature pizza menu
- ✅ Custom Pizza Builder (5 steps: Base → Sauce → Cheese → Veggies → Review)
- ✅ Live price calculation
- ✅ Shopping cart with GST and delivery fee
- ✅ Razorpay Checkout — Test Mode (Card / UPI / COD)
- ✅ Order Tracking — 5-step live status pipeline

### 🛡️ Admin
- ✅ Admin login
- ✅ Dashboard — orders, revenue, pending count
- ✅ Orders management — update status via dropdown
- ✅ Inventory — 16 ingredients, low-stock alerts at <20 units
- ✅ Notifications — auto alerts for stock threshold

## 🖥️ Tech Stack
| Technology | Usage |
|------------|-------|
| HTML5 | SPA structure |
| CSS3 | Dark theme, grid, animations |
| JavaScript | Full app logic, state management |

